30
00:04:51,965 --> 00:04:54,225
This is for Tenshinhan!

31
00:04:56,035 --> 00:05:01,065
How?! How does Kakarrot have this much power?!

32
00:05:01,105 --> 00:05:02,505
What?!

33
00:05:04,275 --> 00:05:07,105
And this is for Piccolo!

34
00:05:10,115 --> 00:05:11,475
Dammit!

35
00:05:33,675 --> 00:05:37,605
Awesome! You really are awesome, Goku!

36
00:05:37,645 --> 00:05:38,835
Yeah!

37
00:05:52,425 --> 00:06:00,055
Dammit! Dammit!

38
00:06:02,665 --> 00:06:06,225
Dammit!

39
00:06:08,075 --> 00:06:11,635
I see... Impressive...
You really are extremely tough, huh?

40
00:06:11,675 --> 00:06:14,635
I am an elite warrior
from a distinguished family!

41
00:06:14,675 --> 00:06:18,645
I'm not about to be looked down
upon by a lower-class warrior like you!

42
00:06:18,685 --> 00:06:21,845
You'll pay for this! I'll kill you!

43
00:06:21,885 --> 00:06:25,415
You miserable fool! Cool that head of yours!

44
00:06:25,455 --> 00:06:27,415
If you'll compose yourself and think about it,

45
00:06:27,455 --> 00:06:30,655
