opponent that you can't take, Nappa!

46
00:06:30,695 --> 00:06:32,455
Calm down!

47
00:06:44,875 --> 00:06:47,405
You're right!

48
00:06:47,445 --> 00:06:50,275
Thanks to you, my eyes have been opened.

49
00:06:52,415 --> 00:06:57,945
<i>That simple-celled fool! At this</i>
<i>rate, it looks like I will have to step in.</i>

50
00:06:57,985 --> 00:07:04,225
It's true, I was pretty upset. Now it's
time to show you what I'm really made of.

51
00:07:04,265 --> 00:07:07,425
Are you ready for this, Kakarrot?!

52
00:07:07,465 --> 00:07:11,625
That's more like it. I can't wait!

53
00:07:11,665 --> 00:07:14,065
Talk tough, will you?

54
00:07:14,105 --> 00:07:19,635
<i>He's not just talking tough. He's got</i>
<i>assurance and absolute confidence in himself.</i>

55
00:07:37,265 --> 00:07:39,385
G-Goku...

56
00:07:39,425 --> 00:07:41,425
Father...

57
00:07:53,005 --> 00:07:57,405
Son<i>-kun</i>, pound that guy into a pulpy mass!

58
00:07:57,445 --> 00:07:58,885
H-Hey!

59
00:08:06,285 --> 00:08:09,015
Hey! Don't be so rough with this!

60
00:08:09,055 --> 00:08:12,185
Who cares if a crystal ball or two gets broken?!

61
00:08:12,225 --> 00:08:15,195
It's an important tool of my trade!

62
00:08:15,235 --> 00:08:19,625
With Kami<i>-sama</i> dead, and us not knowing
whether the Earth will be destroyed or not,

63
00:08:19,665 --> 00:08:22,035
you can just stuff your trade!

64
00:08:22,075 --> 00:08:23,435
How dare you say that!

65
00:08:23,475 --> 00:08:25,835
Now see here!

66
00:08:25,875 --> 00:08:29,275
Would you two quit it?!

67
00:08:29,315 --> 00:08:30,645
It doesn't matter, does it?

68
00:08:30,685 --> 00:08:35,845
Yeah! While you two are at it
there, Goku could be getting done in.

69
00:08:35,885 --> 00:08:39,855
Rubbish! Son<i>-kun</i> is obviously doing all right!

70
00:08:39,895 --> 00:08:44,455
You think he's going to lose
to those guys?! No way! No way!

71
00:08:44,495 --> 00:08:46,455
Don't hit my crystal ball!

72
00:08:46,495 --> 00:08:51,125
Hey, shut up, already! Give that here!

73
00:08:51,165 --> 00:08:54,335
A little brother does not
take his older sister's things!

74
