Whoo! This is a lot better, ain't it?

76
00:10:15,785 --> 00:10:17,585
This is a lot better, huh?

77
00:10:17,625 --> 00:10:21,755
I'm going to put a stop to that
irritatingly smart mouth of yours!

78
00:10:21,795 --> 00:10:24,025
