I-Impossible! That was–that was my
greatest technique, and you brushed it aside!

82
00:11:16,215 --> 00:11:18,545
You really are one tough bastard.

83
00:11:18,585 --> 00:11:21,345
You should have taken at least
a little damage from my Kamehame<i>-Ha.</i>

84
00:11:21,385 --> 00:11:27,185
–We ain't getting anywhere like this.
–Enough! Get down here, Nappa!

85
00:11:27,225 --> 00:11:30,785
