Even that big guy is scared of him.

90
00:11:47,775 --> 00:11:49,875
Father...

91
00:12:33,955 --> 00:12:36,585
D-Dammit...

92
00:12:36,625 --> 00:12:40,925
T-To think that I should have
to yield your execution to Vegeta...

93
00:12:40,965 --> 00:12:48,265
But brace yourself! Your life will
only last for a moment against Vegeta!

94
00:12:48,305 --> 00:12:53,875
He is a warrior gifted enough to take
upon him the name of Planet Vegeta, after all.

95
00:12:53,915 --> 00:12:58,375
Since he ordered me to,
I'll leave you to Vegeta.

96
00:12:58,415 --> 00:13:01,615
But I won't be content to withdraw like this.

97
00:13:10,965 --> 00:13:13,365
Oh, no! He's going after those two!

98
00:13:20,975 --> 00:13:23,465
It's no use! I won't make it in time!

99
00:13:32,185 --> 00:13:35,345
<i>Kaio-ken!</i>

100
00:13:35,385 --> 00:13:36,615
What?!

101
00:13:59,375 --> 00:14:01,775
What just happened?

102
00:14:01,815 --> 00:14:04,175
Goku! How did you–?

103
00:14:09,685 --> 00:14:12,985
Dammit!

104
00:14:19,395 --> 00:14:21,725
I doubt he'll be able to fight anymore.

105
00:14:21,765 --> 00:14:25,595
Take him, and disappear from
the face of the earth right now!

106
00:14:26,765 --> 00:14:32,235
<i>What was that just now?! For an instant,</i>
<i>his speed and power suddenly increased!</i>

107
00:14:36,375 --> 00:14:40,345
G-Goku, how did you do that?

108
00:14:40,385 --> 00:14:44,345
Was that a technique you
learned from that Kaio person?

109
00:14:44,385 --> 00:14:47,785
Yeah. It's called <i>Kaio-ken.</i>

110
00:14:48,395 --> 00:14:53,425
By controlling all of the energy within
your body, you can momentarily amplify it.

111
00:14:56,895 --> 00:14:59,165
If you do it right, your speed, power,

112
00:14:59,205 --> 00:15:02,795
destructive and defensive
forces all increase many times over.

113
00:15:08,945 --> 00:15:10,345
T-That's awesome!

114
00:15:10,385 --> 00:15:12,345
Even after getting that much stronger,

115
00:15:12,385 --> 00:15:14,745
you can become many times stronger than <i>that</i>?!

116
00:15:16,155 --> 00:15:17,385
Yeah.

117
00:15:19,385 --> 00:15:22,755
What are those guys talking about?

118
00:15:22,795 --> 00:15:26,925
Goku, that was mean of you!
This is no time to be playing around.

119
00:15:26,965 --> 00:15:32,365
If you have something like that up
your sleeve, then use it right at the start!

120
00:15:32,405 --> 00:15:34,935
Sorry, but I can't do that.

121
00:15:34,975 --> 00:15:40,465
If I don't restrain my <i>ki</i> just right while
I'm controlling it, I could wreck myself.

122
00:15:42,815 --> 00:15:44,145
In short...

123
00:15:45,415 --> 00:15:48,945
You have done well to
master the <i>Kaio-ken</i> technique,

124
00:15:48,985 --> 00:15:53,815
which even I could not handle,
to this degree. However,

125
00:15:53,855 --> 00:15:59,755
