146
00:18:58,975 --> 00:19:02,965
Both of you, go back to Kame House right now.

147
00:19:15,395 --> 00:19:17,585
R-Right...

148
00:19:17,625 --> 00:19:20,955
Gohan, you heard him. Let's go, now.

149
00:19:20,995 --> 00:19:22,925
B-But...

150
