181
00:22:09,395 --> 00:22:11,795
Father...

182
00:22:14,805 --> 00:22:19,935
<i>Vegeta... Has there ever</i>
<i>been a foe this powerful before?</i>

183
00:22:19,975 --> 00:22:22,705
