00:23:38,185 --> 00:23:43,815
<i>Aah, enough! Even Kami-sama has it rough.</i>

198
00:23:43,855 --> 00:23:45,985
<i>So sorry.</i>

199
00:23:46,025 --> 00:23:51,125
<i>Ooh, full-bellied ZENKAI power!</i>

200
00:23:53,835 --> 00:23:59,105
<i>Come on out, full-on ZENKAI power!</i>

201
00:24:10,115 --> 00:24:11,945
<i>Heya! I'm Goku!</i>

202
00:24:11,985 --> 00:24:14,155
<i>Looks like it's finally</i>
<i>time for us to fight, huh?</i>

203
00:24:14,195 --> 00:24:17,155
<i>You should be thrilled.</i>
<i>A lower-class warrior such as yourself</i>

204
00:24:17,195 --> 00:24:20,285
<i>is about to be toyed around</i>
<i>with by a super-elite, after all.</i>

205
00:24:20,325 --> 00:24:25,395
<i>W-What a ki! It's as if</i>
<i>the whole earth is shaking!</i>

206
00:24:25,435 --> 00:24:27,295
<i>Next time on Dragon Ball Z,</i>

207
00:24:27,335 --> 00:24:31,505
<i>"A Hot, Unbounded Battle!</i>
<i>Goku vs. Vegeta."</i>

208
